Nature Reviews Molecular Cell Biology - January 2014

78 Pages | HQ PDF | English | 11 MB 


Nature Reviews Molecular Cell Biology is a peer-reviewed monthly review journal that was established in October 2000 and is published by Nature Publishing Group. It covers all aspects of molecular and cell biology. According to the Journal Citation Reports, the journal had a 2012 impact factor of 37.162, ranking it first out of 184 journals in the category "Cell Biology".
